article.description: — Jalen Ray had 23 points as Hofstra edged past Richmond 76-71 on Tuesday.
article.headline: Ray scores 23 to lead Hofstra past Richmond 76-71
article.linkText: Ray scores 23 to lead Hofstra past Richmond 76-71
article.story: RICHMOND, Va. -- — Jalen Ray had 23 points as Hofstra edged past Richmond 76-71 on Tuesday. Isaac Kante had 16 points and 11 rebounds for Hofstra (4-3). Tareq Coburn added 15 points and Kvonn Cramer had 12 points. Grant Golden had 15 points and five assists for the Spiders (6-2). Tyler Burton added 15 points and seven rebounds and Blake Francis had 13 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
